{"pin":"BH00822","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00822","anchor":"","first_line":"These are the verses of God, the King, the Truth, the Manifest Justice, which have verily descended from the heaven of a mighty favor; and they are [3.5s]... ...Should any man, in this Day, arise and, with absolute detachment from all that is in the heavens and all that is on the earth, set his affections on Him Who is the Dayspring of God’s holy Revelation","first_line_orig":"تلک آیات الله الملک الحق العدل المبین نزلت بالحق من جبروت فضل عظیم و انها  ","language":"1","word_count":"990","subjects":"@wine as symbol of spiritual transformation, @steadfastness; perseverance; faithfulness, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @suffering and imprisonment, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience, @call to action, @sacrifice of the Manifestation of God redeems the world","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#361\"\u003eLL#361\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fr","lang_name":"French"},{"type":"gleanings","typ